<ab facs="#facs_606_r1l15">denn guts / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> als Jr geleyts ʒu vns begert / VVenn Jr denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_606_r1l16"><expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vııȷ tag nach <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchıerıſtkünft<ex>ig</ex></expan> ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wellet </ab>
